metadata.name: Andy's (RE)iteration
metadata.description:
In 2020 one of Pixellitist's earliest mints was a digital recreation of Andy Warhol's famous Mao portrait. 
Since then the piece has been bought, sold and resold with no loss only gain in value. 

This current piece is a most recent iteration, one of a cross-chain series entitled "Andy's Iterations" which debuted on Tez then found it's way to Rarible and now this modified generation has landed on Foundation as a 1 of 1 genesis piece of this 2022 collection. Commemorating the Mao recreation which also use height mapping as a style aesthetic.  

This will be the only Andy's Iterations minted on Foundation.

Peace & Pixels.
